Perceptor::

Perceptor roared annoyed when he see at Warhead wounded he considered 
left him there but thought a second it wasn't a good idea, not for 
his plans and for Predacons' glory.

He moved quickly where Warhead was while he opened fire against SS.




--- In nbwrpg@y..., Kyle Stewart <dewboy30816@y...> wrote:
> SS crawled over to Burok.
> 
> SS:  I need to get back to the base.....help me, I'm
> too weak to fly.
> 
> --- warriorazure <wingedwarrior41@h...> wrote:
> > The gunfire hitting the ground under which the
> > wormbot stood revealed 
> > him. He immediately transformed back to robot mode
> > andhopped out of 
> > his hole. He fired at Inferno's gun as precisely as
> > he could and threw 
> > his tentacules at the antbot's legs, trying to smash
> > him hard to the 
> > ground. His eyes were full of fury as he saw that
> > already, SS was 
> > down, but Warhead was in an even worse condition.
> > 
> > The predacon warrior was lying on his back. Four
> > holes passing through 
> > him marked where the lasers had burned their way.
> > His agony was still 
> > lasting, though, and the pain he endured was
